ewy tannins and a flavorful finish. Decadent. Cabernet franc.</div></div>, <div class=""pipProfessionalReviews_review""><div class=""pipSecContent_copy""><p>Aromas and flavors of black currant, bell pepper, cedar and lead pencil shavings abound in this red. Expressive and elegant, with a supple texture matched to a firm backbone of tannins and acidity. Offers a lingering spicy aftertaste. Cabernet Franc. Drink now through 2028.</p></div></div>]",https://www.wine.com/product/le-macchiole-paleo-2016/620626,italy,red,tuscany
